===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A member of an [[army]], of any rank.
# A guardsman.
# A member of the Salvation Army.
# {{UK}} A piece of [[bread]] (or [[toast]]) and [[butter]], cut into long thin strips and used to eat a [[boiled egg]].
# A term of affection for a young boy.

